ime":"2018-07-19T17:45:30.000Z","msg":"how"},{"pid":"5bf1f13f73a80054276c9218eec633bb66d5d876","tid":749092,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"341188c2d5835f5c044d3cf824783f5cef2ffed9","tid":749092,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"364a7ad5e83f4ff91627f0b8c0de34ea22e1f19c","tid":749092,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f4fbd31484d722fc0a78585929ca949d6639ca3","tid":749092,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T17:38:45.000Z","msg":"搵D興趣，搵D朋友食吓飯，得閒上來吹二句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T17:40:14.000Z","msg":"搵朋友，你地會group定單對單"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T17:41:45.000Z","msg":"算 好麻煩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T17:48:14.000Z","msg":"搵吓人啦，否則放假嘅日子好難過"},{"pid":"09606206809abc7d47d68b86e6236075da0a88e0","tid":749092,"uid":5205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T17:48:42.000Z","msg":"有時想做女仔，享受曬香港啲優惠<br />\n<br />\n追女仔好難，香港人太多唔鍾意人多地方人多完全無空間比我講野<br />\n<br />\n朋友之間傾計又答唔到嘴<br />\n<br />\n又成日諗好耐<br />\n<br />\n老實講 講足球世界盃 我興趣又唔係到 <br />\n今次都算有做下功課同到fd 傾 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我成日覺得自己弱智 溝通障礙<br />\n<br />\n人類好複雜好麻煩<br />\n<br />\n有時又好暴躁 對住沙發拳打腳踢<br />\n<br />\n出街 落雨 啲庶又撞黎撞去<br />\n人又撞黎撞去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都只係想...<br />\n識到一個互相鍾意對方既女仔姐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好簡單 <br />\n<br />\n超想砍掉 重來"},{"pid":"aa751260ea2d0f807095182651c98870f9780c86","tid":749092,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T17:50:38.000Z","msg":"自言自語 <br />\n生存係世上一秒都覺得浪費"},{"pid":"f0899a3a58a355180b3d2e93f11fd7c9957f13fd","tid":749092,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T17:52:15.000Z","msg":"有劇本咪算 最好唔好煩。<br />\n<br />\n聽咩歌好"},{"pid":"4a125227cf68e9b323278bc14804ab4f95b52a20","tid":749092,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T17:53:11.000Z","msg":"有劇本後知道結果會仲灰"},{"pid":"f38f4a017c680b7e3a1301acae86a71ac00f0779","tid":749092,"uid":5205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f0899a3a58a355180b3d2e93f11fd7c9957f13fd","tid":749092,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T17:52:15.000Z","msg":"有劇本咪算 最好唔好煩。<br />\n<br />\n聽咩歌好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T17:54:48.000Z","msg":"日文 港歌 我都唔知 只係知個世界 下下個名氣  <br />\n<br />\n好似平淡就係錯，唔開心就喊 唔想面對工作。唔想面對人類身份 做粒微塵咪算<br />\n<br />\n又要食 住 訓 屙 不如無出過世咪幾好 哈 哈"},{"pid":"ea846735d42c722c1e720f2dd2905d532f9aa122","tid":749092,"uid":5205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T17:58:58.000Z","msg":"係一間有露台既餐廳 係平靜唔多人既 坐位<br />\n<br />\n飲住杯充滿回憶同力量既百事，<br />\n<br />\n覺唔覺女性人類依家走個個方向錯曬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知好想有理想居住地點 但根本無可能就唔想生存"},{"pid":"1f4674180ea6fbbc61c360b1e7481aaab2c50e62","tid":749092,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T18:00:17.000Z","msg":"實有人話我痴左線 ，其實我都認同 我只係偽裝緊正常一般人....我已經玩完"},{"pid":"d84e963bc27e23e4157185fa7ca06504a80eb7e1","tid":749092,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T18:01:25.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"1bc1ee07e27c90877d57ff62af983c5dfcbfe995","tid":749092,"uid":2364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T18:03:37.000Z","msg":"老老實實 一星期一次你都計到，即係你有排都未到痴線"},{"pid":"ba068781b9b7208ac655f63d7a72bfa81316db01","tid":749092,"uid":138670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T18:05:15.000Z","msg":"我都會成日自言自語 人地睇落冇乜意思<br />\n但用嚟發泄，鬧下自己，又勸下自己都幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}